Items.c: <[>該死！我不是擺脫他們了嗎？他們是怎麼追到這裡的！？......說什麼都要讓小狗子他們逃走才行。<]>
Items.mt: <[>Damn! Didn't I get rid of them? How did they get here? ...... I had to let the puppies get away before I could say anything. <]>
